data.description: ATTENTION Investors and 1st time home buyers, this property is  PRICED TO SELL!  Built in 2005 and listed below market value. This warm and inviting home features 4 beds, 2 full baths is 1671 sq feet and sits on .193 ac. When you enter the home to the right is your kitchen with dishwasher, disposal, range and pantry. To your left is your 4th bedroom that can also be an office. Then walk straiht into your open living room with a beautiful rock fireplace to keep you warm on those cold winter nights. To your right is the master suite and to the lrft you will find 2 other bedrroms and another full bath (with ADA Bars). Step out into the enclosed sunroom or go out into the backyard to enjoy some Texas BBQ while you sit around the fire. Don't wait!Come make this home your very own.
